---
const contactHref = '/contact/';
---
<section class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-sm text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-900">Siap Mengubah Bisnis Anda?</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 font-light text-gray-500 md:text-lg">Hubungi kami sekarang untuk konsultasi gratis dan temukan bagaimana AI dapat membantu bisnis Anda.</p>
            <a href={contactHref} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none:ring-blue-800">Konsultasi Gratis</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
